      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fort_Drum"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "A 10‑month, $20 million construction effort built an entire city of 3,000 buildings to house troops at Pine Camp.",
